A python library for working with The Hit List

Requirements:
    The Hit List: http://www.potionfactory.com/thehitlist/
    py-appscript: http://appscript.sourceforge.net/py-appscript/doc/appscript-manual/index.html
    
Examples:
    Several examples are provided in the /examples directory

Scripts:
    Task-oriented scripts are available in /scripts

Tests:
    A simple test suite can be run from /scripts/test.py

